OL,3,CManchester City says goodbye to Pep
OL,4,CGuardiola and celebrates achievements
OL,6,FITV Granada Report's Mike Hall was on
OL,7,Fthe parade route.
OL,9,FManchester City have celebrated
OL,10,Fsuccess by their men's, women's and
OL,11,Facademy sides - and given long-term
OL,12,Fmanager Pep Guardiola an emotional
OL,13,Ffarewell.
OL,15,FCelebrations kicked off with an open-
OL,16,Ftop bus parade in Manchester's
OL,17,FNorthern Quarter, ending at the Etihad
OL,18,FStadium, before the after-party at the
OL,19,FCo-op Live Arena.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
