OL,3,CManchester City says goodbye to Pep
OL,4,CGuardiola and celebrates achievements
OL,6,FPep Guardiola's side secured a
OL,7,Fhistoric domestic cup double, even
OL,8,Fthough they narrowly missed out on the
OL,9,FPremier League title - finishing
OL,10,Fsecond behind Arsenal.
OL,12,FCity's Women had a historic, record-
OL,13,Fbreaking season under manager Andree
OL,14,FJeglertz. They were crowned Super
OL,15,FLeague champions for the first time in
OL,16,Fexactly a decade.
OL,18,FMeanwhile, the youth and academy teams
OL,19,Fclinched two major honours this
OL,20,Fseason: the FA Youth Cup and under-18
OL,21,FPremier League North.
OL,26,@uD@crr
