OL,3,CManchester City says goodbye to Pep
OL,4,CGuardiola and celebrates achievements
OL,6,FThe parade will be Pep Guardiola's
OL,7,Flast, after a decade-long reign at
OL,8,FCity.
OL,10,FHe has enjoyed one of the most
OL,11,Fsuccessful managerial spells in
OL,12,FEnglish football history, having won
OL,13,F20 trophies, including six Premier
OL,14,FLeague titles and the Champions League.
OL,16,FFans said the celebrations have been
OL,17,Fmet with mixed emotions.
OL,19,FFans reacted to the day's celebrations
OL,20,Fwith mixed emotions.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
