OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1779786323
OL,3,CManchester City says goodbye to Pep
OL,4,CGuardiola and celebrates achievements
OL,6,FOne fan said he was "heartbroken" at
OL,7,FPep's departure. He said: "He's done
OL,8,Fso much for me, I can't put it into
OL,9,Fwords."
OL,11,FAnother fan said: "It feels great,
OL,12,Fmost of my life, Pep has been manager
OL,13,Fand we've had so much success with him
OL,14,Fas manager. I'm also excited to see
OL,15,Fwhat the new manager will come in and
OL,16,Fdo and see how the new era will
OL,17,Funfold."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/4
